---
// Projects.astro
---
<section class="projects" id="projetos">
  <div class="projects-header">
    <div>
      <p class="col-label">Portfolio</p>
      <h2>Projetos recentes</h2>
    </div>
    <a href="/projetos" class="projects-link">Ver todos os projetos</a>
  </div>

  <div class="project-card">
    <div>
      <span class="project-tag">Ativo</span>
      <p class="project-name">FinPlan</p>
      <p class="project-meta">Finanças pessoais</p>
    </div>
    <p class="project-desc">
      Aplicativo de gestão financeira pessoal com categorização automática, metas e relatórios de fluxo de caixa. Construído para simplificar a relação com o dinheiro no dia a dia.
    </p>
    <div class="project-cta">
      <a href="/projetos/finplan" class="btn-ghost">Ver projeto →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects {
    padding: 96px 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26, 25, 22, 0.08);
    background: var(--color-ivory);
  }

  .projects-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .col-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .projects h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
  }

  .projects-link {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(119, 109, 95, 0.4);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    transition: color 0.2s ease, border-bottom-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .projects-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-obsidian);
  }

  .project-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(26, 25, 22, 0.08);
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .project-card:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26, 25, 22, 0.08);
  }

  .project-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-mint);
    color: var(--color-grove);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .project-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .project-meta {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .project-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .project-cta {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26, 25, 22, 0.2);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    background: var(--color-obsidian);
    color: var(--color-ivory);
    border-color: var(--color-obsidian);
  }

  /* Tablet: 768px – 1024px */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .projects {
      padding: 72px 40px;
    }
    .projects h2 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }
    .project-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .project-cta {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile: até 767px */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .projects {
      padding: 56px 24px;
    }
    .projects h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .projects-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .project-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 32px 0;
    }
    .project-name {
      font-size: 22px;
    }
  }
</style>
